        </item>
        <item>
            <title>世博展全球首部 AI 自动洗澡机   15 分钟完成洗澡超疗愈感受</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/27/ai-bath-tube/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ai-bath-tube</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/27/ai-bath-tube/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 27 Apr 2025 08:23:40 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1305117</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>2025 年大阪世博会上，日本企业 Science 正式展示他们的 AI 自动洗澡机「ミライ人间洗濯机」，结合人工智能与感应技术，让洗澡成为一场身心灵放松的疗愈旅程。这部外形酷似战机驾驶舱的装置，利用智能系统即时调节水流和温度，并播放短片，让使用者在短短 15 分钟内享受多感官的舒缓体验。设计灵感取自 1970 年大阪万博展示过的超声波浴缸，展望未来生活方式的同时，也为洗浴设备注入崭新元素。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/06screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305126" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/06screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/06screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/06screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>这台 AI 自动洗澡机外观设计充满未来感，拥有一个可开启的透明罩，吸引大量参观者驻足观赏。当体验者跨入机舱，透明罩缓缓关闭，洗澡过程正式展开。整个过程由 AI 系统全程监控，透过感应器即时测量使用者心跳、情绪等身体数据，并根据个人状况灵活调整水流强度与水温，确保每位使用者获得最适合自身状态的洗浴体验。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/034screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305119" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/034screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/034screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/034screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/037screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/037screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/037screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/037screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开始注水</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/052screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/052screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/052screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/052screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲利用感应器测量心跳，根据精神状态播放音乐和影像</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/058screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305123" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/058screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/058screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/058screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲浴缸内充满洁白的泡沫</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/115screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1305124" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/115screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/115screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/115screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲微细气泡技术可产生泡沫，将污垢浮起并冲洗全身</p><p>透明罩正面设有显示屏幕，除了即时反映使用者的身体状态数据，还同步播放舒压短片，令整个洗澡过程更加放松。该机器备有三种模式可供选择，包括展现日本四季景色的庭园、五彩缤纷的海底世界，及辽阔无垠的鸟瞰天空，让每次洗澡都能依心情自由切换，享受视觉与身体的双重放松。</p><p>Science 董事长青山恭明指出，这款洗澡机采用公司自家开发的 Mirable 微细气泡技术，有效洁净皮肤同时呵护肌肤健康。他强调，这部洗澡机不单向 1970 年大阪万博展出的超声波浴缸致敬，更期望透过科技改善日常生活质素，开启未来洗浴新时代。</p><p>目前 Science 已开放 1000 个体验名额，全数成功登记。未来是否投入市场销售，仍有待进一步公布。这款 AI 自动洗澡机展示了日本企业在结合科技与生活层面的创新思维，为日常沐浴习惯带来全新可能。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_35717"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dyw6s1n3n_k?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/04/27/ai-bath-tube/ai/">世博展全球首部 AI 自动洗澡机   15 分钟完成洗澡超疗愈感受</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/27/ai-bath-tube/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
